t’s new in AVFoundation","type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc21-10146-whats-new-in-avfoundation","abstract":[{"text":"Discover the latest updates to AVFoundation, Apple’s framework for inspecting, playing, and authoring audiovisual presentations. We’ll explore how you can use AVFoundation to query attributes of audiovisual assets, further customize your custom video compositions with timed metadata, and author caption files.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC21-10146-Whats-new-in-AVFoundation"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"title":"Learn More…","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Learn More…","type":"text"}],"type":"link"},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10140":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2021\/10140","type":"download","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2021\/10140","checksum":null},"WWDCNotes.png":{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","alt":null},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC21-10225-Coordinate-media-experiences-with-Group-Activities":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC21-10225-Coordinate-media-experiences-with-Group-Activities","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover how you can help people watch or listen to content all in sync with SharePlay and the Group Activities framework. We’ll show you how to adapt a media app into a synchronized, SharePlay-enabled experience for multiple people. Learn how to add Group Activities to your app, explore the Picture in Picture layout, and find out how the playback coordinator object can help you fine-tune playback across multiple devices."}],"